name: family with sequence similarity 90 member A3
other_names: family with sequence similarity 90 member A3, pseudogene
summary: FAM90A3 belongs to subfamily II of the primate-specific FAM90A gene family, which originated from multiple duplications and rearrangements (Bosch et al., 2007 [PubMed 17684299]). For background information on the FAM90A gene family, as well as information on the evolution of FAM90A genes, see FAM90A1 (MIM 613041).[supplied by OMIM, Oct 2009].
